  <brief_title>Transdermal Fentanyl Patch for Postoperative Analgesia After Abdominal Surgery: a Randomized Placebo-controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transdermal Fentanyl Patch for Postoperative Analgesia After Abdominal Surgery: a Randomized Placebo-controlled Trial</official_title>
